Implement the complete reconcile function including:
1. State machine transitions (Pending -> Provisioning -> Loading -> Ready -> Scaling -> Draining -> Terminating)
2. Idempotent node provisioning using node affinity and taints
3. Model weight loading detection via readiness probe on /health/model endpoint
4. HPA-equivalent logic reading from a custom queue-depth metric
5. Graceful shutdown: stop accepting new requests, drain in-flight requests with 30s timeout, then terminate
6. Proper use of finalizers for cleanup
7. Status condition updates at each transition

Also identify three subtle bugs or design flaws in the existing CRD spec that would cause problems in production.
